---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import { createPageMeta, SITE_CONFIG } from '../utils/meta';
const metaData = createPageMeta('/soporte', {
  title: `Soporte — ${SITE_CONFIG.name}`,
  description: 'Centro de ayuda de Tutreino. Encontrá respuestas rápidas o contactá a nuestro equipo de soporte.',
  noindex: false,
});
---
<SiteLayout {...metaData}>
  <main class="h-legal-wrap">
    <div class="h-legal-inner">
      <a href="/" class="h-legal-back">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        Volver al inicio
      </a>

      <header class="h-legal-header">
        <span class="h-legal-eyebrow">Soporte</span>
        <h1 class="h-legal-h1">¿En qué podemos <span class="h-grad">ayudarte?</span></h1>
        <p class="h-legal-lead">Encontrá respuestas rápidas o contactá directamente a nuestro equipo. Estamos para ayudarte.</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Canales de contacto rápido -->
      <section class="sp-section">
        <h2 class="sp-section-title">Contacto directo</h2>
        <div class="sp-channels">
          <a href={SITE_CONFIG.appRegistrationUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="sp-channel sp-channel--primary">
            <div class="sp-channel-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/><path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.124.554 4.118 1.523 5.847L0 24l6.305-1.506A11.945 11.945 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 21.818a9.818 9.818 0 01-5.006-1.368l-.36-.213-3.732.892.924-3.644-.234-.374A9.818 9.818 0 112 12 9.818 9.818 0 0112 21.818z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-channel-body">
              <span class="sp-channel-label">WhatsApp</span>
              <span class="sp-channel-desc">Soporte prioritario para clientes. Respondemos al instante en horario hábil.</span>
              <span class="sp-channel-badge">Más rápido</span>
            </div>
            <svg class="sp-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </a>

          <a href="mailto:soporte@tutreino.com" class="sp-channel">
            <div class="sp-channel-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-channel-body">
              <span class="sp-channel-label">Email</span>
              <span class="sp-channel-desc">soporte@tutreino.com — respondemos en menos de 24 horas hábiles.</span>
            </div>
            <svg class="sp-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <section class="sp-section">
        <h2 class="sp-section-title">Preguntas frecuentes</h2>
        <div class="sp-faq">

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Cómo agrego un nuevo socio a mi gimnasio?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>Desde el panel de administración, ingresá a la sección <strong>Socios</strong> y hacé clic en <strong>+ Nuevo socio</strong>. Completá el nombre, email y plan. El socio recibirá un email de bienvenida con acceso a la app.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Cómo configuro los pagos recurrentes?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>En <strong>Configuración → Pagos</strong> podés vincular tu cuenta de MercadoPago o Stripe. Una vez conectado, cada plan puede tener cobro automático mensual o según el ciclo que definas.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Los socios pueden ver sus rutinas desde el celular?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>Sí. Cada gimnasio tiene su propia app con tu logo y colores. Los socios descargan la app, inician sesión y acceden a sus rutinas, historial y reservas en tiempo real.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Puedo exportar los datos de mis socios?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>Sí. En <strong>Socios → Exportar</strong> podés descargar un CSV con todos los datos: nombre, email, plan, estado de pago y fecha de ingreso.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Qué hago si un socio no puede acceder a la app?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>Verificá que el email del socio esté correctamente cargado en el panel. Si el problema persiste, podés reenviarle el email de acceso desde <strong>Socios → Detalle → Reenviar invitación</strong>. Si sigue sin funcionar, contactanos por WhatsApp.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="sp-faq-item">
            <summary class="sp-faq-q">
              <span>¿Cómo cancelo mi suscripción?</span>
              <svg class="sp-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="sp-faq-a">
              <p>Podés cancelar desde <strong>Configuración → Suscripción → Cancelar plan</strong>. Si necesitás ayuda o querés hablar antes de cancelar, escribinos por WhatsApp — nos interesa entender qué pasó.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Info adicional -->
      <section class="sp-info-strip">
        <div class="sp-info-item">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <div>
            <span class="sp-info-label">Horario de soporte</span>
            <span class="sp-info-val">Lun–Vie, 9:00 – 18:00 (UTC-3)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-info-divider"></div>
        <div class="sp-info-item">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 10.8a19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 012 0h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 7.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 14.9v2.02z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <div>
            <span class="sp-info-label">Tiempo de respuesta</span>
            <span class="sp-info-val">WhatsApp: inmediato · Email: &lt;24 h</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-info-divider"></div>
        <div class="sp-info-item">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <div>
            <span class="sp-info-label">Tus datos están seguros</span>
            <span class="sp-info-val">Nunca compartimos tu información con terceros</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
/* ── Sections ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sp-section {
  margin-bottom: 56px;
}
.sp-section-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mute);
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}

/* ── Contact channels ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sp-channels {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}

.sp-channel {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
  padding: 20px 22px;
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--ink);
  transition: border-color .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease, transform .18s ease;
}
.sp-channel:hover {
  border-color: var(--line-2);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15,22,35,0.07);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.sp-channel--primary {
  border-color: var(--green);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--green) 4%, var(--panel));
}
.sp-channel--primary:hover {
  border-color: var(--lime);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px color-mix(in srgb, var(--green) 20%, transparent);
}

.sp-channel-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: var(--bg-2);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  color: var(--green);
}
.sp-channel-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
.sp-channel--primary .sp-channel-icon {
  background: var(--green);
  border-color: var(--green);
  color: white;
}

.sp-channel-body {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
}
.sp-channel-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--ink);
}
.sp-channel-desc {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: var(--mute);
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.sp-channel-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  width: fit-content;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--green) 12%, transparent);
  color: var(--green);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.sp-arrow {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  color: var(--mute);
  transition: color .18s ease, transform .18s ease;
}
.sp-channel:hover .sp-arrow {
  color: var(--green);
  transform: translateX(3px);
}

/* ── FAQ ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sp-faq {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--panel);
}

.sp-faq-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.sp-faq-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.sp-faq-q {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 20px 24px;
  cursor: pointer;
  list-style: none;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  transition: background .15s ease, color .15s ease;
  user-select: none;
}
.sp-faq-q::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
.sp-faq-q:hover {
  background: var(--bg-2);
  color: var(--green);
}
.sp-faq-item[open] .sp-faq-q {
  color: var(--green);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--green) 4%, var(--panel));
}

.sp-faq-chevron {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  color: var(--mute);
  transition: transform .22s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1), color .18s ease;
}
.sp-faq-item[open] .sp-faq-chevron {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  color: var(--green);
}

.sp-faq-a {
  padding: 0 24px 20px;
  animation: sp-expand .2s ease;
}
.sp-faq-a p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  color: var(--ink-2);
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.sp-faq-a strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

@keyframes sp-expand {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── Info strip ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sp-info-strip {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
  padding: 28px 32px;
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.sp-info-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  flex: 1;
}
.sp-info-item svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  color: var(--green);
  opacity: 0.8;
}
.sp-info-item div {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}
.sp-info-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mute);
}
.sp-info-val {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: var(--ink-2);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.sp-info-divider {
  width: 1px;
  height: 40px;
  background: var(--line);
  margin: 0 32px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

@media(max-width:820px) {
  .sp-info-strip {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .sp-info-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    margin: 0;
  }
}

@media(max-width:480px) {
  .sp-faq-q { padding: 16px 18px; font-size: 14px; }
  .sp-faq-a { padding: 0 18px 16px; }
}
</style>
